is a fictional character in the manga series Death Note , created by Tsugumi Ohba and Takeshi Obata .
He is a bored Shinigami that drops a Death Note , a notebook that allows you to kill anyone simply by knowing their name and face , into the human world in order to have fun .
It is picked up by Light Yagami , a young genius who uses it in an attempt to create and rule a utopia cleansed of evil , with him at the helm as a `` god '' .
In the anime adaptation , Ryuk is voiced by Nakamura Shidō in Japanese and by Brian Drummond in the English version .
Both actors reprise their roles for voicing the computer-generated version of the character in the live-action films , with Jun Fukushima voicing the CG version in the live-action television drama .
In the musical , Ryuk was portrayed by Kōtarō Yoshida .
Actor Willem Dafoe will voice the character in the American adaptation .